{"tid":1270863,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"點解TVB同班偽人咁囂張？因為你哋從來冇認真抵制過佢哋","createTime":"2019-07-01T03:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T09:17:29.000Z","uid":15696,"like":254,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fda11376d7d2dc52e62871cb3482cd883706948d","tid":1270863,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:22:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">話以後唔睇TVB新聞，去睇倚天屠龍記同愛回家。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前話唔睇曾志偉啲戲，一出啲垃圾賀歲片，有人去睇。出咗一念無明，個個爭住入場。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要做，就要做到足。你可能會話香港抵制冇用，佢哋仲有大陸市場。<br />\n<br />\n但係我哋要做嘅，唔係令佢冇飯開（冇可能），而係透過票房、收視點撃，同佢哋講：</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你冇資格代表香港人！<br />\n</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你冇資格代表香港人！梁家輝！<br />\n</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你冇資格代表香港人！譚詠麟！<br />\n</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你冇資格代表香港人！陳百祥！鍾鎮濤！劉美君！<br />\n</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4fbe1b4f2e7bba174de73ed161c5b7d91008d4a1","tid":1270863,"uid":15696,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:24:03.000Z","msg":"我哋要用行動你哋冇資格代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n風林火山？所有你哋有份嘅嘢，我唔會睇！"},{"pid":"7aece9ffc25a55bcbd3c1d3d6ebc85b8df0c1a5c","tid":1270863,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7d12791c68a3b96b6e0b5a1fa79e9e83d1a86b","tid":1270863,"uid":15696,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:25:34.000Z","m